<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-68-0333 </DOCNO><TEXT>The book contains three studies dealing with pricing policies on the gasolinemarket of the Federal Republic of Germany, cost calculation and legalaspects exemplifying Paragraph 27(2) AVBV, and the portfolio managementof the supply industry. The studies intend to facilitate access to thediverse and many-coloured spectrum of the non-guided and guided energymarket or supply industry, respectively. The particular problems presentedare looked at from different economic points of view. (orig./UA)</TEXT></DOC>